{"tid":1100363,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"近9年美斯225次當選全場最佳，比C朗拿度多100次","createTime":"2019-04-10T10:47:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T15:02:01.000Z","uid":20634,"like":22,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"81199d7f1d3a1b3abf1ec554cecbc9de94b6a807","tid":1100363,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T10:47:42.000Z","msg":"從2010-11賽季開始至今，美斯一共225次當選全場最佳，是所有球員中當選全場最佳次數最多的，他比排名第二的C朗拿度足足多了100次。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/asKgdqp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FasKgdqp.png&h=9555b09a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nC朗拿度以125次全場最佳排名第二，夏薩特93次當選排名第三，排名第四的是伊巴謙莫域，他89次當選全場最佳，接着是尼馬和蘇亞雷斯，他們兩人都是65次當選全場最佳，巴利62次當選全場最佳排名第七，之後的是基沙文58次，維達爾53次，列奧斯50次。<br />\n<br />\n過去9年美斯和C朗拿度一直難分高下，但在當選全場最佳次數這個數據上，美斯完勝了C朗拿度。在排名前十的球員中，多數都來自西甲，夏薩特是唯一一位當前在英超踢球的球星。"},{"pid":"1017959f65fa9c18a30fc9ded731663293013995","tid":1100363,"uid":155902,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T10:51:46.000Z","msg":"西甲唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴塞唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866709e9517e68945a875445af71ac730903240b","tid":1100363,"uid":20634,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T11:16:23.000Z","msg":"梅西唔敢雞姦証明自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4bd2ae1d8b3bf1f2841bf982604cfa9dc2cda1e","tid":1100363,"uid":151933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T11:17:06.000Z","msg":"2頁"},{"pid":"8f9b0fe7ce96d771fe38f912fc4162f0323435d8","tid":1100363,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T11:20:00.000Z","msg":"唔係咩叫溫室小花 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a393020cb684f645b80926b75e720b1203693ae","tid":1100363,"uid":172226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"81199d7f1d3a1b3abf1ec554cecbc9de94b6a807","tid":1100363